ion fee until you find out if your request for a waiver is granted or not if we deny your request for a waiver we will instruct you to pay the fee refunds are not given to applicants who pay for the application themselves instead of using their granted application fee waivers application fee and payment up apply using the online application groups office of graduate admissions printer friendly version calendar quick links academic calendar stanford bulletin explorecourses diversity in graduate education policy statements askjane student services center copyright 2011 stanford university terms of use copyright complaints report a problem with this site
